title: Scholar Athlete of the Week: Canterbury's Kate White
text:
Scholar Athlete of the Week: Canterbury's Kate White 
By WISE Web News October 16, 2015 Updated Oct 16, 2015 at 11:16 AM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, Ind. (21Alive) â€“ The 21Alive/Parkview Sports Medicine Scholar Athlete of the Week for Oct. 15 is Canterbury High School senior Kate White. 
White is a four-sport student-athlete: playing soccer and running cross country in the fall, swimming in the winter and running track & field in the spring. 
She has a 4.4 grade point average. 
White plans to attend Duke University, and study engineering.
